{"tid":1948814,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"哲學家齊澤克 教你抗疫三式﹕互助、煲劇、尋找生命意義","createTime":"2020-03-29T08:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T09:51:30.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb3316a28cdc4d015f65606b3fdabdd484179cbc","tid":1948814,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:48:07.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情嚴重，全球多國強制或勸籲市民減少出門。著名學者齊澤克 (Slavoj Zizek) 昨日撰文，談隔離期間人們該如何自處。他認為，互助能助人減低精神壓力。若無法互助，則不必考慮太多，做自己喜歡的事，煲劇也無所謂。然而最重要的，還是在疫情中，尋找生命的意義。<br />\n<br />\n齊澤克坦言，自己喜歡宅在家閱讀與工作，平時就算去旅行，也喜歡留在酒店，而不去旅遊景點。「對我來說，一篇關於著名畫作的好文章，意義遠比在人多的博物館看這幅畫深遠。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E9%BD%8A%E6%BE%A4%E5%85%8B%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E4%B8%89%E5%BC%8F-%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A9-%E7%85%B2%E5%8A%87-%E5%B0%8B%E6%89%BE%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E9%25BD%258A%25E6%25BE%25A4%25E5%2585%258B%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25BC%258F-%25E4%25BA%2592%25E5%258A%25A9-%25E7%2585%25B2%25E5%258A%2587-%25E5%25B0%258B%25E6%2589%25BE%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2591%25BD%25E6%2584%258F%25E7%25BE%25A9%2F&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJezv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=53dfc35e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E9%25BD%258A%25E6%25BE%25A4%25E5%2585%258B%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25BC%258F-%25E4%25BA%2592%25E5%258A%25A9-%25E7%2585%25B2%25E5%258A%2587-%25E5%25B0%258B%25E6%2589%25BE%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2591%25BD%25E6%2584%258F%25E7%25BE%25A9%2F&h=666ac421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E9%BD%8A%E6%BE%A4%E5%85%8B%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E4%B8%89%E5%BC%8F-%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A9-%E7%85%B2%E5%8A%87-%E5%B0%8B%E6%89%BE%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9/</a><br />\n<br />\n原文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rt.com/op-ed/48